{"tid":600793,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(放負）入嚟講吓有咩事你係一直都做得唔好","createTime":"2018-03-21T15:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T15:42:39.000Z","uid":125434,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"026d8b9530a2051c323fc612b0d48a5c1fc12d51","tid":600793,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一直以嚟，自己係一個好中意搞創作嘅人，邊方面嘅創作都中意（H漫都可以寫吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 但係一直都無好好嘗試同經營，同時又覺得自己好無料，唔敢搵人一齊合作去做<br />\n<br />\n結果人大了，又唔係有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n面對生活，好似愈嚟愈無火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c28151c21133888fffebc7dd6868d4f4176331e","tid":600793,"uid":30259,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:40:31.000Z","msg":"完美A+，零錯別字，肥絲好波"},{"pid":"35b4fa35d15dee79c43f025d88b05065ba90bdd9","tid":600793,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:40:32.000Z","msg":"想做一個細心嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後都係一個大頭蝦"},{"pid":"32911249513044869c181f8f389d6a595ff3dc9e","tid":600793,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"絲打唔好噉快氣餒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到我分享：<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己喺同人建立關係嘅時候，太易對人好，但唔係個個受。<br />\n男嘅會嫌我煩，女嘅會俾我嘅好嚇親，吃不消。<br />\n有時我重會因為噉而俾人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211a0cbe8bb59a8ce9b33d68ae3bb21d7008407b","tid":600793,"uid":144312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"未試過做得好，一切一切"},{"pid":"b13b5ec865439190cf5c5d6abbf79c9c0e98ba18","tid":600793,"uid":170616,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"211a0cbe8bb59a8ce9b33d68ae3bb21d7008407b","tid":600793,"uid":144312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018